---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Grandevity Limited"
  lang="en"
  description="Learn about Grandevity Limited, the New Zealand company behind Grandevity Studio, Grandevity Music, original HTML5 games, digital architecture, and modern music releases."
>
  <main class="about-container">
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1>About <span class="text-gradient">Grandevity</span></h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Engineering Digital Worlds with Precision and Purpose.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="about-content">
      <section class="mission-section">
        <h2>Our DNA</h2>
        <p>Grandevity Limited is a digital studio proudly incorporated in New Zealand and the company behind Grandevity Studio and Grandevity Music. We operate at the unique intersection of robust system architecture, original interactive entertainment, and modern music releases inspired by classical Chinese literature.</p>
        <p>Our philosophy is simple: whether we are designing a complex web application, analyzing digital compliance structures, or building a 60-FPS HTML5 tower defense game, the underlying principles remain the same. It requires structural integrity, optimized performance, and a deep respect for the end-user's experience.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="what-we-do-section">
        <h2>What We Build</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon">🎮</div>
            <h3>Original Games</h3>
            <p>We develop lightweight, highly optimized HTML5 games like <em>Kiwi Defenders</em>. By utilizing vanilla web technologies, we deliver instant, cross-platform interactive experiences without the bloat of heavy commercial game engines.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon">🎵</div>
            <h3>Grandevity Music</h3>
            <p>Grandevity Studio releases modern Mandopop and R&B works that reimagine classical Chinese poetry for contemporary listeners across global Chinese-speaking audiences.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon">⚙️</div>
            <h3>Digital Architecture</h3>
            <p>Drawing from deep expertise in enterprise resource planning (ERP) systems and strict regulatory compliance frameworks, we approach software design with an emphasis on scalability, security, and logical elegance.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon">💡</div>
            <h3>Technical Insights</h3>
            <p>Through our Insights Hub, we share our ongoing research and development logs. We explore topics ranging from artificial intelligence behaviors in gaming to the humanities and historical system designs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="company-details">
        <h2>Corporate Information</h2>
        <div class="details-box">
          <p><strong>Legal Entity:</strong> Grandevity Limited</p>
          <p><strong>Jurisdiction:</strong> New Zealand</p>
          <p><strong>NZBN (New Zealand Business Number):</strong> 9429053472120</p>
          <p><strong>Business Focus:</strong> Digital Product Development, Interactive Media, and Technology Consulting</p>
          <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@grandevity.co.nz">info@grandevity.co.nz</a> <em></em></p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container { 
    padding: 4rem 5%; 
    max-width: 1000px; 
    margin: 0 auto; 
    min-height: 70vh; 
    color: #cbd5e1;
  }
  .about-header { 
    text-align: center; 
    margin-bottom: 4rem; 
  }
  .about-header h1 { 
    font-size: 3.5rem; 
    margin-bottom: 1rem; 
    color: #f8fafc; 
  }
  .text-gradient { 
    background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #38bdf8, #818cf8); 
    -webkit-background-clip: text; 
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; 
  }
  .subtitle { 
    color: #94a3b8; 
    font-size: 1.2rem; 
  }
  
  .about-content h2 { 
    color: #f8fafc; 
    font-size: 2rem; 
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem; 
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .about-content p { 
    line-height: 1.8; 
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem; 
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
  }
  .feature-card .icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .feature-card h3 {
    color: #38bdf8;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .company-details {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }
  .details-box {
    background: #0f172a;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #38bdf8;
  }
  .details-box p {
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .details-box a {
    color: #38bdf8;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .details-box a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>